expt_aim: Level of comfortness in mathematics in comparison to actual mathematical skill.
expt_gen: A lot of the first part of the study talks a lot about anxiety over studying for a mathematics test. I don't know if this is of any value, but I think it's important to note that people who love mathematics also get a lot of anxiety over mathematics tests too. Especially when you get to high level math like real analysis, combinatorics, complex linear algebra, etc. That's how I feel at least, though I'm sure you guys have taken that into account anyways.
